# Component Patterns

## Sidebar (L1)
- BG: `bg-[#e7f1f8]`, Width: `w-[88px]`, Nav icon: `size-6`, active: `bg-[#b1e6fb]`, hover: `hover:bg-[#e0e0e0]`
- Label: `text-[10px] leading-[12px]`, bold when active
- Icon pattern: duo-tone (`fill="white"` body, `stroke/fill="#101010"` details) — see `design-system-icons.mdc`

## L2 Submenu
- Position: `left-[88px]`, Width: `w-[236px]`, BG: `bg-[#e7f1f8]`, border-l `border-[#e0e0e0]`, `rounded-tr-[16px]`
- Shadow (when open): `shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(0,0,0,0.15)]`
- Category title: `text-[12px] tracking-[0.6px] uppercase font-semibold text-[#101010] leading-[16px]`, no hover on title
- Chevron (collapsible only): `size-6 text-[#101010]`, hover only on icon `hover:bg-[#e0e0e0]`
- Items: `p-[12px] rounded-[12px] hover:bg-[#e0e0e0]`, active: `bg-[#b1e6fb]`
- Item icon: `size-6 text-[#101010]`, Item label: `text-[14px] font-medium leading-[20px] text-[#101010]`
- Click outside closes, smooth transitions

## Dashboard Metric Cards
- Payments: `bg-[#F5FBFE]`, Settlement: `bg-[#F0FDF4]`, Refunds: `bg-[#FEF2F2]`
- Border radius: `rounded-[20px]`, padding: `p-5`, divider: `border-t border-border pt-3`

## Action Cards
- P0: `bg-[#ffebef]/60`, P1: `bg-[#fff8e1]/60`, hover: full opacity
- No border/stroke, `rounded-lg`, `p-4`, `transition-colors`

## Buttons (Button_v2)
- All: `rounded-[8px] font-semibold transition-colors`, centered text+icon layout
- Props: `emphasis` (High|Medium|Low), `size` (Large|Medium|Small), `icon` (None|Leading|Trailing|Both|Only), `state` (Normal|Hover|Loading), `enabled` (bool)

### Emphasis Levels
- **High (Primary)**: `bg-[#004299] text-white` · hover: `hover:bg-[#009de5]`
- **Medium (Secondary)**: `border border-[#004299] text-[#004299]` · hover: `hover:bg-[#e7f1f8] hover:border-[#009de5] hover:text-[#009de5]`
- **Low (Tertiary)**: `bg-[#e7f1f8] text-[#004299]` · hover: `hover:bg-[#f5f9fe] hover:text-[#009de5]`

### Sizes
- **Large**: `p-4 min-w-[120px] text-[16px] leading-[20px]` → height 56px
- **Medium**: `px-4 py-2.5 min-w-[120px] text-[14px] leading-[20px]` → height 40px
- **Small**: `px-4 py-2 min-w-[80px] text-[12px] leading-[16px]` → height 32px

### States
- **Disabled**: `bg-[#ebebeb] text-[#acacac] opacity-64 cursor-not-allowed` (all emphasis levels)
- **Loading**: replace label with animated dots, same container styling

### Icon Variants
- Leading/Trailing: icon + label in row, `gap-2`
- Both: leading icon + label + trailing icon
- Only: square button (56×56 / 40×40 / 32×32), icon centered, no label

## Hyperlinks
- **Strong** (primary action links — "Create an account", "View All", "Learn More"): `text-[#004299] hover:underline font-semibold`
- **Subtle** (secondary/auxiliary links — "Forgot Password", "terms of use", "privacy policy"): `text-[#004299] hover:underline font-normal`
- Default size: `text-[12px]` in body copy, `text-[14px]` for standalone links

## TextField (Text Field_v2) — Single Source of Truth for Text/Input Fields
Shared floating-label input component (`src/app/components/TextField.tsx`), matching the Figma `Text Field_v2` spec. **This is the only text/input field component in the UMP component library.** All form text inputs, password fields, email fields, URL fields, date fields, and textareas MUST use this component.

### When to Use
- Login forms (email, password with eye toggle via `trailingIcon`)
- Payment Pages forms (page info, settings, property panels)
- Popup form fields (via `PopupInput` which wraps `TextField`)
- Any form that collects text input from the user

### When NOT to Use
- Search bars (Header, SearchWithDropdown, dashboard filters) — these are standalone search components with different visual patterns (pill shape, inline icon, no floating label)
- Checkboxes, toggles, radio buttons — these are separate components
- File upload inputs — use the dedicated upload zone component
- Select/dropdown menus — use `SelectField` or native `<select>`

### Container
- Height: 56px (`size="default"`), 44px (`size="compact"` for panels) — **same height in all states** (idle, focus, filled)
- Border radius: `rounded-[4px]`
- Border: 1px solid `#e0e0e0` (Normal/Filled), `#004299` (Hover/Focus), `#fd5154` (Error)
- Background: `bg-white` (Normal), `bg-[#ebebeb]` (Disabled)
- Padding: **16px** left/right (`px-[16px]`), **8px** top/bottom (`py-[8px]`)

### Internal Layout (Filled/Focus state)
- Label container height: **16px** (`leading-[16px]`)
- Input value container height: **24px** (`leading-[24px]`)
- Layout: 8px top padding + 16px label + 24px value + 8px bottom padding = **56px**

### Floating Label States
- **Normal (empty, unfocused)**: Label centered, `text-[14px] font-semibold text-[#7e7e7e]`
- **Hover**: Same as Normal, border changes to `#004299`
- **Focus (empty)**: Label floats to top-left, `text-[12px] font-normal text-[#7e7e7e]`, border `#004299`
- **Focus Filled**: Label floated, input text visible, border `#004299`
- **Filled (unfocused)**: Label floated, input text visible, border `#e0e0e0`
- **Disabled**: `bg-[#ebebeb]`, `text-[#acacac]`, `cursor-not-allowed`

### Variants
- **Error**: border `#fd5154`, error text below in `text-[12px] text-[#fd5154]`
- **Assistive text**: hint below in `text-[12px] text-[#101010]`
- **Prefix**: left-aligned prefix (e.g., `paytm.com/`) in `bg-[#fafafa]` with `border-r`
- **Trailing icon**: right-aligned icon slot (e.g., password visibility toggle)
- **Multiline**: textarea mode with `rows` prop
- **Compact**: `size="compact"` for property panels (44px height, `text-[13px]`)

### Props
```tsx
interface TextFieldProps {
  label: string;
  value: string;
  onChange: (value: string) => void;
  type?: "text" | "email" | "url" | "number" | "password" | "date";
  disabled?: boolean;
  error?: string;
  assistiveText?: string;
  required?: boolean;
  prefix?: string;
  trailingIcon?: React.ReactNode;
  multiline?: boolean;
  rows?: number;
  size?: "default" | "compact";
}
```

### Usage across the project
- **LoginPage**: `<TextField label="Mobile Number or Email" />`, `<TextField label="Paytm Password" type="password" trailingIcon={<Eye/>} />`
- **PageInfoForm**: All fields (Form Name, URL Path with prefix, HTML Title, etc.)
- **AdditionalSettings**: Redirect URL, Success Message (multiline), SMS Text (multiline), Email fields
- **PropertyPanel**: Compact variant for component properties
- **PopupInput**: Wraps `TextField` for popup form contexts

## Device Cards (My Services)
- Card: `bg-white border border-[#e0e0e0] rounded-[12px] p-5`, header has title left + "View All" hyperlink right
- Sub-items: `bg-[#fafafa] hover:bg-accent/50 rounded-[8px] p-3`, gap between items: `gap-3` (12px)
- Icon container: `size-10 rounded-[8px] bg-[#e0f5fd]`, product icons at `size-10` using `currentColor`
- Status text: due=`text-[#ff9d00]`, paid=`text-[#21c179]`

## Service Cards (Grow your Business)
- Card: `bg-white border border-[#e0e0e0] rounded-[12px] p-5 flex flex-col gap-4`, hover: `hover:bg-[#f5f9fe]`
- Icon container: `size-10 rounded-[8px] bg-[#e0f5fd]`, product icons at `size-8` or `size-10`
- Title: `text-[14px] font-semibold text-[#101010]`
- Body: `text-[12px] text-[#7e7e7e] leading-[18px]`
- CTA: Secondary CTA button with `ArrowRight` icon (`size-3.5`)
- Status chip (optional): `px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-[12px] font-semibold`
- Layout: `grid grid-cols-2 gap-6`
- Enabled service flow: when a service is enabled, its card moves from "Grow your Business" to the "My Services" section (below device cards), constrained to first-column width via `grid grid-cols-2 gap-6` wrapper, with status chip and updated CTA

## Connect Plus Activation Flow
- Default: "Get Started" CTA in Grow your Business grid → opens form popup
- Form popup: checkbox consent → "Accept and Continue" CTA
- Loader popup: `type="loader"`, no close button, auto-dismisses after 6s
- After loader: opens new tab + sets enabled state on current page
- Enabled: card moves to My Services section with "Enabled" chip + "Open Connect Plus" CTA

## Paytm Logo
- On dark backgrounds (`bg-[#004299]`, overlays, branded headers): use entirely white logo — all SVG paths `fill="white"`, no accent colors
- Position: top-left of the container
- Size: `w-[100px] h-[34px]`, wrapped in `relative shrink-0`

## Authorization Page
- Layout: standalone full-screen page (NO sidebar, NO header), card centered on `bg-[#f5f9fe]` background
- Route: top-level route outside `AppShell`, renders without any navigation chrome
- Page wrapper: `flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen bg-[#f5f9fe] p-6`
- Card: `bg-white w-[620px] rounded-[4px] overflow-hidden`
- Branded header: `bg-[#004299]`, white Paytm logo top-left, `gap-[28px]` between logo and title+email group
- Title+email grouped with `gap-3`; app name highlighted in `text-[#00b8f5]`
- Permission icons: `bg-[#fafafa]` (neutral), not `bg-[#e0f5fd]`
- Checkbox consent: no background card, `items-center` alignment, checkbox + text inline with `gap-3`
- Checkbox text: `text-[12px] leading-[20px]`
- Disclaimer lines: `gap-0` between them, first line `text-[12px]`, second line `text-[10px]`
- Buttons: Cancel (Medium) and Authorize (High) — both `flex-1` for equal width
- Footer bar: sky blue `#00b8f5` (8px) + navy `#012a72` (8px) strip at bottom

## Payment Pages (SwiftPay Builder)

### Dashboard (`/payment-pages`)
- Follows standard page pattern: `px-[32px] pt-[12px] pb-[32px] bg-white min-h-full`
- Action bar: "Create Page" Primary CTA (High emphasis, `Plus` icon) + search + filters (Status, Date)
- Table: `grid-cols-[1.5fr_1.5fr_1fr_0.8fr_0.8fr_0.4fr]`, without vertical separators
- Status chips: Active `text-[#21c179] bg-[#e3f6ec]`, Expired `text-[#fd5154] bg-[#ffebef]`, Draft `text-[#7e7e7e] bg-[#fafafa]`
- Actions: kebab menu (Share, Download QR, Edit, Expire/Reactivate, Delete)

### Create Page Entry
- Popup (`type="form"`) with 4 option cards: Build from Scratch, Select Template, Copy Existing, Build with AI
- Each card: `border border-[#e0e0e0] rounded-[12px] p-5 hover:bg-[#f5f9fe]`, icon in `size-10 rounded-[8px] bg-[#e0f5fd]`

### Step Wizard
- 3 steps: Page Information → Page Builder → Additional Settings
- Active: `bg-[#004299] text-white` circle, Completed: `bg-[#21c179]` with check, Upcoming: `bg-[#e0e0e0]`
- Steps connected by `h-[2px]` lines (green if completed, grey otherwise)

### Step 1: Page Information
- Centered form (`max-w-[640px]`), fields: Form Name, URL Path (prefixed), HTML Title, Support Contact/Email, Freeze Date
- All inputs use the shared `TextField` component (floating-label, 56px, `rounded-[4px]`)
- Cover Image has moved to Step 2 (Page Builder) as a draggable palette component

### Step 2: Page Builder
- Three-panel layout: Component Palette (`w-[280px]`) | Builder Canvas (`flex-1`) | Property Panel (`w-[320px]`)
- Palette: categorised draggable components (Display, Layout, Input, Choices, Date, Pricing, Verification, Address, eCommerce, Other)
- Display category includes **Cover Image** (drag-and-drop upload zone, PNG/JPG up to 5MB)
- Canvas: `bg-[#fafafa]`, drop zone highlights `border-[#004299] bg-[#f5f9fe]`, selected component: `border-[#004299]`
- Input previews on canvas use floating-label style: `h-[56px] border border-[#e0e0e0] rounded-[4px]`
- Properties: Label, Placeholder, Required/Show (Always/Never/When), toggles, Options list, Validation (Min/Max Length, Regex)
- HTML5 Drag and Drop API (no external dependency)

### Step 3: Additional Settings
- Primary tabs: Post Transaction | Notifications
- Post Transaction: Redirect URL, Success Message
- Notifications: SMS toggle + text, Email toggle + subject + body
- "Save & Publish" button uses success green: `bg-[#21c179] hover:bg-[#1aa866]`

## Popup / Modal
- Container: `bg-white w-[620px] max-h-[90vh] rounded-[4px] overflow-hidden`
- Overlay: `bg-[#101010]/70` (strong) or `bg-[#101010]/13` (weak)
- Close button: `size-8 rounded-[4px] hover:bg-[#f5f9fe]`, icon `size-6 text-[#101010]`
- Title: `text-[32px] font-bold leading-[36px] text-[#101010]`
- Subtext: `text-[14px] leading-[20px] text-[#101010]`
- Form content padding: `px-8`, gap: `gap-8` between sections
- Footer bar: sky blue `#00b8f5` (8px) + navy `#012a72` (8px) strip at bottom
- Types: `status` (centered), `form` (left-aligned), `loader`, `share`

## Tabs

### Primary Tabs
- Active: `text-[18px] font-bold text-[#004299]` + 4px underline `bg-[#004299]`
- Inactive: `text-[18px] font-normal text-[#101010]`, no underline
- Hover: `text-[18px] font-normal text-[#101010]` + 4px underline `bg-[#e0e0e0]`
- Gap between tabs: `32px`, full-width 1px `bg-[#e0e0e0]` separator below
- Optional badge: `bg-[#004299]` pill, `text-[10px] font-medium text-white`

### Secondary Tabs
- Height: `h-[32px]`, `rounded-[8px]`, `px-[12px] py-[4px]`
- Gap between tabs: `16px` (default), configurable via `gap` prop
- Active: `bg-[#004299] text-white font-semibold text-[14px]`
- Inactive (Flat): `bg-[#f5f9fe] text-[#101010] font-normal text-[14px]`
- Inactive (Outlined): `bg-white border border-[#cacaca] text-[#101010] font-normal text-[14px]`
- Hover (Flat): `bg-[#e0e0e0]`
- Hover (Outlined): `border-[#7e7e7e]`
- Optional badge: active=`bg-white text-[#004299]`, inactive=`bg-[#004299] text-white`

## Search with Dropdown
- Container: `bg-white border border-[#e0e0e0] rounded-lg h-[40px]`, default `w-[560px]`
- Dropdown: `text-[14px] font-semibold text-[#101010]`, `hover:bg-[#f5f9fe]`, chevron toggle
- Divider: `w-[1px] bg-[#e0e0e0]` full height
- Search input: `text-[14px] font-semibold text-[#101010]`, placeholder `text-[#7e7e7e]`, search icon `size-5 text-[#7e7e7e]`

## Table/Listing
- Container: `overflow-x-auto border border-[#e0e0e0] rounded-[12px]`, inner min-width wrapper: `min-w-[700px]`
- Layout: CSS Grid with `grid-cols-[...]` (column ratios vary per use case)
- Header: `border-b border-[#e0e0e0]`, text: `text-[12px] uppercase tracking-[0.6px] font-semibold text-[#7e7e7e] leading-[16px]`
- Row cells: `px-6 py-4`, data: `text-[14px] text-[#101010] leading-[24px]`
- Row hover: `hover:bg-[#f5f9fe] transition-colors`
- Row borders: `border-b border-[#e0e0e0]` between rows; last row has NO bottom border (outer container border suffices)
- Border radius: `rounded-[12px]` on container with `overflow-hidden` if needed

### Variant: With Vertical Separators
- Vertical lines run end-to-end through the full height of the listing frame (not short inline dividers)
- Implementation: apply `border-r border-[#e0e0e0]` on each cell EXCEPT the last column
- Padding (`px-6 py-4` for rows, `px-6 py-3` for header) goes on individual cells, NOT on the grid row
- Grid row has NO horizontal padding — cells own their own padding

```tsx
{/* Header */}
<div className="grid grid-cols-[1fr_1.5fr_0.5fr] border-b border-[#e0e0e0]">
  <p className="... px-6 py-3 border-r border-[#e0e0e0]">Column A</p>
  <p className="... px-6 py-3 border-r border-[#e0e0e0]">Column B</p>
  <p className="... px-6 py-3">Column C</p>
</div>
{/* Row */}
<div className="grid grid-cols-[1fr_1.5fr_0.5fr] hover:bg-[#f5f9fe] border-b border-[#e0e0e0]">
  <div className="px-6 py-4 border-r border-[#e0e0e0]">...</div>
  <div className="px-6 py-4 border-r border-[#e0e0e0]">...</div>
  <div className="px-6 py-4">...</div>
</div>
```

### Variant: Without Vertical Separators
- No vertical dividers between columns
- Padding (`px-6 py-4` for rows, `px-6 py-3` for header) goes on the grid row
- Cells have no individual padding or borders

```tsx
{/* Header */}
<div className="grid grid-cols-[1fr_1.5fr_0.5fr] border-b border-[#e0e0e0] px-6 py-3">
  <p className="...">Column A</p>
  <p className="...">Column B</p>
  <p className="... text-right">Column C</p>
</div>
{/* Row */}
<div className="grid grid-cols-[1fr_1.5fr_0.5fr] px-6 py-4 hover:bg-[#f5f9fe] border-b border-[#e0e0e0]">
  <div>...</div>
  <div>...</div>
  <div>...</div>
</div>
```

### Rules
- DO use CSS Grid (`grid grid-cols-[...]`) for column layout — not flexbox or `<table>`
- DO keep the last row without `border-b` to avoid doubling with the outer container border
- DO NOT use short inline `<div>` separators for vertical lines — use cell `border-r` for end-to-end lines
- DO NOT put `px-6` on grid rows when using vertical separators — put padding on cells instead

## Payment Settings — Charges Section

The Settings → Payment Settings page uses a Table/Listing (with vertical separators, `grid-cols-[1fr_1.5fr_0.5fr]`) to display payment instruments, their charges, and status across QR, Card Machine, and Payment Links tabs.

### Charges Column Content Rules
- All charges text uses `font-weight: 400` (normal) — **never** apply `font-semibold` to charges content or its container
- Tiered pricing uses `<div className="flex flex-col gap-1">` wrapper with one `<p>` per tier line
- Tier label (muted): `<span className="text-[#7e7e7e]">Up to ₹20,000 / month : </span>`
- Tier value (default): `<span className="text-[#101010]">3% + GST</span>`
- Single-value charges: `<span className="text-[14px] text-[#101010]">1.99% + GST</span>`
- Free charges: `<span className="text-[#21c179]">Free</span>` (success green, no bold)
- Indented sub-tiers: add `ml-4` to the `<p>` element

### Hyperlinks Inside Charges
- "View Special Cards" / "Know More" links follow the standard Hyperlink pattern: `text-[#004299] text-[12px] font-semibold hover:underline`
- Hyperlink `font-semibold` is the **only** bold text allowed in the charges column — it applies to the `<a>` element only, never to charge amounts or labels

### Charges Content Pattern
```tsx
charges: (
  <div className="flex flex-col gap-1">
    <p className="text-[14px] leading-[24px]">
      <span className="text-[#7e7e7e]">Up to ₹20,000 / month : </span>
      <span className="text-[#101010]">3% + GST</span>
    </p>
    <p className="text-[14px] leading-[24px]">
      <span className="text-[#7e7e7e]">More than ₹20,000 / month : </span>
      <span className="text-[#101010]">4% + GST</span>
    </p>
    <a href="#" className="text-[#004299] text-[12px] font-semibold hover:underline mt-1">
      View Special Cards - Amex, Diners and Rupay
    </a>
  </div>
)
